{
  "id": "adv_card_ai_10_03",
  "title": "小美山愛 3話 学んだことを噛みしめて",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――花火大会当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Fireworks Festival Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 1.4866666079
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "は～、緊張しますね\n一人のお仕事もそれなりに経験してきたのになぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah~‚ I'm nervous.\nEven though I've had a fair bit of experience with solo work~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.2999999206
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、凄くワクワクもしてます\n私のパフォーマンスをお客さんに喜んでもらいたくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I'm also really excited.\nbecause I want the audience to enjoy my performance.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.3999999206
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "愛なら大丈夫。立派にやり遂げられるよ\n……なぁ、愛。今更だけど、聞いてもいいか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You'll be fine‚ Ai. You'll do a great job.\n…Hey‚ Ai. It's a bit late‚ but can I ask you something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "はい、なんでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ what is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.5333332539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "最初の打ち合わせの前に、泣いていただろ\n……理由を聞いてもいいか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were crying before the first meeting‚ weren't you?\n…Can I ask why?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.9999999206
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ！？　見られちゃってたんですね、恥ずかしいです\n……あ。だから私のこと、心配してくれてたんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh!? You saw that? How embarrassing.\n…Oh. That's why you were worried about me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.3454811898,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんに心配を掛けてしまって\n本当にすみません……あの、本当になんでもなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm really sorry for making you worry‚ {user}-san…\nUm‚ it really wasn't anything serious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.5666658243
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4になってお仕事が忙しくなって\nちょうどあの頃、夜間の収録が続いていて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After I became BIG4‚ work got really busy‚\nand around that time‚ because of continuous night recordings―",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.7999992371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "それで元気がなかったのか……\nすまない、愛。俺がもっと気を付けていれば――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that's why you seemed down…\nSorry‚ Ai. If I had been more careful--",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.7333325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.3666648071
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "お父さんのラーメンが\n二週間も食べられなかったんです……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "― I couldn't eat dad's ramen\nfor two whole weeks…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.2666659038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "…………え？　お父さんの、ラーメン？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "………Eh? Dad's… ramen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.0000011922,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.4333345255
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　日中は学校があるし、土日もお仕事があるし\n仕事が終わると、もう出掛けていい時間じゃないし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! I have school during the day‚ and work on weekends‚\nand by the time work ends‚ it's already too late to go out…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.0333325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "インスタントやカップ麺では誤魔化せないほど\nお父さんのラーメンが恋しくなっちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I started missing dad's ramen so much\nthat instant or cup noodles just couldn’t satisfy me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.2457836152,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.7000011922
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-ai010.m4a",
      "text": "お父さんにその弱音を聞いてもらってたんです\nだから本当に、深刻な話じゃなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was having dad listen to my complaints.\nSo it really wasn't a serious matter…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.4474614108,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.1666678589
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "じゃ、じゃあ……\nこの間廊下でため息をついていたのは……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-then…\nThe sighing in the hallway the other day was…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.6999992371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 106.2333345255
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-ai011.m4a",
      "text": "それはまた別の話なんですけど、えっと……花火大会の\nことを調べているうちに、つい寂しくなっちゃって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's a different matter‚ but… while researching\nthe fireworks festival‚ I couldn't help feeling lonely.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.9666659038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-ai012.m4a",
      "text": "調べるほど、凄く楽しそうで……莉央さん達と四人で\n来たかったなって、ちょっとだけ思っちゃったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The more I researched‚ the more fun it seemed…\nI kind of wished all four of us could've come together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.4999992371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.9333345255
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-ai013.m4a",
      "text": "最近プライベートではなかなか時間が合わないし……\n今回のお仕事も、私一人になっちゃいましたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Lately‚ we haven't had much time together in private.\nAnd this job ended up being just me alone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.7333325704,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことだったのか……ごめん、気付かなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that's what it was… Sorry I didn't notice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.3666678589,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 140.6000103475
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-ai014.m4a",
      "text": "いえいえいえ！　こちらこそ心配を掛けちゃって\n本当にすみませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No no no! I'm the one who made you worry.\nI'm really sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.8333417257,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-ai015.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんを困らせないようにって\n黙ってたのに、結局困らせちゃうなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I kept quiet so I wouldn't trouble {user}-san‚\nbut I ended up troubling you anyway.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.4000083924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.9000103475
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-ai016.m4a",
      "text": "でも、もう大丈夫です。莉央さん達は来れなくても\n私にはファンの方々や、大切な人達がいてくれますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it's okay now. Even though Rio-san and the others can't come‚\nI have the fans and precious people with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.9666750591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.6666770142
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-ai017.m4a",
      "text": "……あっ、話し込んでるうちに、リハの時間ですね\n{user}さん、行きましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Oh‚ while we were talking‚ it became rehearsal time.\n{user}-san‚ let's go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 166.2333417257,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "愛……。あぁ、一件連絡だけ済ませたら、俺も行くよ\n先に行っててくれるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ai… Okay‚ I'll come too after I finish one phone call.\nCan you go ahead?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.2000083924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-ai018.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました、慌てずに来て下さいね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Understood‚ please come without rushing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.2333436808,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3866.6647116000095,
