      "text": "みなさーん！　もうすぐ花火が打ち上がりますよー！\nそれに合わせて、次が最後の曲になります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone! The fireworks will be launched soon!\nIn time with that‚ the next song will be the last one!",
        "id": ""
