      "text": "私のパフォーマンスが、今日の思い出を彩って\nこの歌を聴くたびに、この夜空を思い出してくれたら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If my performance colors today's memories‚\nand you remember this night sky every time you hear this song‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 203.7666689556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-ai021.m4a",
      "text": "私も、本当に嬉しいです！　もし機会をいただけるなら\n今度はリズノワ四人で立てるように願いを込めて――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I would be really happy! With the hope that\nall four of us from LizNoir can perform together next time――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 213.5666689556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_feststage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "feststage-00-night",
      "startTime": 217.6000357789
    },
    {
