      "text": "……愛が気付いたみたいだな。莉央さん、葵、こころ\n今日は駆けつけてくれてありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Looks like Ai noticed. Rio-san‚ Aoi‚ Kokoro.\nThank you for rushing over today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 230.7666689556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "なんとか間に合ったな\n直前の仕事のスケジュール、調整出来て良かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We somehow made it in time.\nI'm glad we could adjust the last-minute work schedule.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 235.5333356222,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_feststage-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "feststage-00-night",
      "startTime": 239.1000357789
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
