    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、連絡したら駆けつけてくれたよ\nさぁ、これに着替えて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone rushed over when I contacted them.\nCome on‚ change into this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 264.5000022889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 266.8000459514
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-ai026.m4a",
      "text": "これ、って……浴衣！？\nえ、私のですか！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is… a yukata!?\nEh‚ is it for me!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 270.5333356222,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 273.0000459514
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "愛は凄く頑張っていたし、随分我慢してただろ？\n今日はみんなで花火を見て、出店を回って、帰りは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You worked really hard‚ Ai. And you endured a lot‚ didn't you?\nToday we'll all watch the fireworks‚ go around the stalls‚ and on the way home…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 277.4333356222,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 282.3333792848
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-ai027.m4a",
      "text": "……ラ、ラーメン！？　いいんですか！？\nこころも葵さんも莉央さんも！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…R-ramen!? Is that okay!?\nKokoro‚ Aoi-san‚ and Rio-san too!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 285.5666689556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "今日は俺のおごりだ\n四人で遠慮なく、思いっきり楽しんでくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll treat you today.\nAll four of you‚ don't hold back and have a great time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 290.4333356222,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 294.1333792848
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-ai028.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ……！　ありがとうございます！\nすぐに着替えてきますから、外で待ってて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow…! Thank you so much!\nI'll change right away‚ so please wait outside!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 298.5000022889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
