      "startTime": 303.1833792848
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-ai029.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、私今、最高の気分です\n……本当は今日、ちょっぴり心細かったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ I'm feeling the best right now.\n…Actually‚ I was feeling a little anxious today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 310.3000022889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-ai030.m4a",
      "text": "以前の私なら、余裕をなくして迷惑を掛けてました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it were the old me‚ I would have lost my composure and caused trouble.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 314.9000459514,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-ai031.m4a",
      "text": "でも、今まで{user}さんから\n学んだことを一つ一つ噛みしめて、凄く頑張ったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I took everything I've learned\nfrom {user}-san‚ and worked really hard.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 322.6333356222,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "そうだったのか。……愛、ラーメンのトッピング\n『全部乗せ』してもいいからな。ほんのお詫びだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… Ai‚ you can have all the toppings\non your ramen. It’s just a little apology.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 332.5000022889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ai_10_03-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "（愛はBIG4として、立派に成長していたんだな）\n（今までとは別の意味で、目が離せないほどに）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ai has grown admirably as BIG4.）\n（I can't take my eyes off her in a different way than before.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 341.6666689556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
